Carol Vorderman, 61, put her jaw-dropping curves on display in a slinky skintight dress last night. The Countdown star took to Instagram ahead of her son Cameron’s graduation to show off her outfit. She uploaded a series of mirror selfies, featuring a close-up look at the dress and her staple smokey eye makeup. Carol captioned one of the snaps: “My son’s graduation this evening….best wear a dress.” The TV star paired the blue maxi dress with some nude stilettos and accessorised the outfit with a gold necklace. The pictures also gave fans an insight into Carol’s impressive walk-in closet. The ageless beauty also shared the pictures on her main feed, where fans were able to leave comments heaping praise on her outfit.